{{codepointer|Classic attack}}'''A_SpawnSound'''
{{doomwiki|A_SpawnSound}}

(no parameters)

{{note|text=This function has been superseded by [[A_PlaySound]], which duplicate and extend its functionality. Use of the newer functions is advised in order to maintain maximum flexibility in your code.}}

Plays the sound “brain/cube” on the “Body” channel and calls [[A_SpawnFly]] without parameters. This function is kept for [[DEHACKED]] compatibility and should not be used for new projects.

